s you try to make enough room for some medding hmmm.Don't try to quad kite around a crowded area player wise either..inevitably a warrior will stick his nose in an break your beautiful chain you had going...do it in quiet zones or times...and as i read in another post here it's not about being the best druid in the game just be the best Druid you can be and have fun            Lvl 52 Human Druid on MM</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Mith&nbsp;&nbsp;Marr               Server of champions</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >4 Replies</td></tr></table>
